From what i understand the sump only has one
disadvantage and that is the reduction of ground
clearance. I do wish i had Thoms' "problem", who
wouldn't want a westy hitch! The sump provides an
extra quart and a half and in an aircooled vw that
isn't a bad thing to have. I have one and a doghouse
set-up in my 65 Westfalia and have NEVER overheated my
bus! 

Sean Dorman
